metadata.name: For Carl Salomon
metadata.description:
1/1 minted by Athena Novo, Playground Athena smart contract on Manifold, 2022

Playground Athena has no structure. It is not built on any plans. No consistency is required. No modus operandi is specified. No method concerns encompass. Moments where states and moods can shift quickly are tolerated. We're all in Rockland here. We're all Carl Salomon.
